# Virtual Environment

The project virtual environment is located at `venv/` in the root of the repository.

Always activate it before running any Python commands:

```powershell
# Windows (PowerShell)
venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

```bash
# Unix/macOS
source venv/bin/activate
```

Never run `python`, `pip`, or any project scripts without the venv active.
